00:20:37,050 --> 00:20:39,451
Especially in free-to-play games, but really all games,

403
00:20:40,011 --> 00:20:43,112
are driven by intense activity from outliers.

404
00:20:43,552 --> 00:20:46,113
And their presence or absence in any piece of data

